high_descs: In kitchen turn right and turn left to the sidetable again turn right to the bedroom.
Take a mug from the table. Turn right, turn left, and turn right to reach the sink.
Put the cup in the sink. Pour the water and wash it.
Take a mug from the sink.
Turn left and move upwards to the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, place the mug in the cupboard and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Pick the mug, clean it and place it on the cabinet.

Pick up the mug from the end table.
Walk out of the bedroom, down the hallway, into the kitchen and over to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug into the kitchen sink, run the water to wash it, then pick up the mug after.
Move slightly to the left and look up to the cabinets above the kitchen sink.
Open the door to the cabinet, place the coffee mug to the left of the container, and then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a Mug to put away in the kitchen Cabinet.
